OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774685151
OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FIsrael launched a fresh wave of
OL,7,Fstrikes on Iran early on Friday
OL,8,Fmorning as US President Donald Trump
OL,9,Fextended his deadline for the regime
OL,10,Fto reopen the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FTrump announced on Thursday evening
OL,13,Fthe US would hold off on bombing
OL,14,FIran's energy plants for a further 10
OL,15,Fdays, as "per Iranian government
OL,16,Frequest", adding that talks between
OL,17,Fthe two countries were going "very
OL,18,Fwell".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
