FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774685151
OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FThe president had first vowed to
OL,7,Fstrike Iran's power plants if Iran did
OL,8,Fnot fully reopen the Strait of Hormuz
OL,9,F- a vital waterway through which a
OL,10,Ffifth of the world's oil passes - last
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,FHowever, he then postponed the strikes
OL,14,Fby five days on Monday, amid
OL,15,F"productive conversations" on ending
OL,16,Fthe war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
