CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774685151
OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FThe US delivered Iran a 15-point
OL,7,Fproposal for a ceasefire earlier this
OL,8,Fweek, but has also ordered thousands
OL,9,Fmore troops to the region at the same
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIran has since shared its five-point
OL,18,Fdemands for the conflict to end, which
OL,19,Fincludes reparations and recognition
OL,20,Fof its sovereignty over the Strait of
OL,21,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
