CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774685151
OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FThe UN Security Council will hold a
OL,7,Fmeeting to discuss attacks on Iranian
OL,8,Fcivilian infrastructure on Friday
OL,9,Fmorning, while oil prices rose again
OL,10,Fto $107 a barrel, up more than 45%
OL,11,Fsince the war began.
OL,13,FSince the war began, more than 1,900
OL,14,Fpeople have been killed in Iran,
OL,15,Faccording to the Health Ministry,
OL,16,Fwhile 1,100 people have died in
OL,17,FLebanon, 18 in Israel and at least 13
OL,18,Fservice members from the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
