OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FIn Iraq, 80 members of security forces
OL,7,Fhave been killed, with Iranian-
OL,8,Fsupported militia groups carrying out
OL,9,Fattacks in the country.
OL,11,FIsrael attacks Iran and Lebanon as
OL,12,FGulf nations report missiles
OL,14,FIsrael said it would be "intensifying"
OL,15,Fits strikes on Iranian weapons
OL,16,Fproduction facilities, as it launched
OL,17,Fan attack on targets "in the heart of
OL,18,FTehran" on Friday morning.
