CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774685151
OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,F"As per Iranian Government request,
OL,7,Fplease let this statement serve to
OL,8,Frepresent that I am pausing the period
OL,9,Fof Energy Plant destruction by 10 Days
OL,10,Fto Monday, April 6, 2026, at 8 P.M.,
OL,11,FEastern Time," the US president wrote.
OL,13,F"Talks are ongoing and, despite
OL,14,Ferroneous statements to the contrary
OL,15,Fby the Fake News Media, and others,
OL,16,Fthey are going very well."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
