OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FEarlier on Thursday at a White House
OL,7,Fcabinet meeting, Trump claimed Iran
OL,8,Fwas "begging" to make a deal, as he
OL,9,Flaunched a tirade against NATO for
OL,10,Fdoing "absolutely nothing" to help
OL,11,Fwith the war.
OL,13,FHe later told Fox News Iran had asked
OL,14,Ffor a seven-day pause, but he decided
OL,15,Fto give them 10 days, claiming Iranian
OL,16,Fofficials were "very thankful".
