OL,3,CIran under Israeli fire as Trump
OL,4,Cpushes back Strait of Hormuz deadline
OL,6,FThe Trump administration also
OL,7,Fconfirmed the 15-point plan it
OL,8,Fpresented to Iran, which includes
OL,9,Fshutting down Iran's nuclear
OL,10,Ffacilities and limiting its missile
OL,11,Fcapabilities.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
